-------------------------------------------
INSTALL instructions for OpenCity 0.0.3stabe
-------------------------------------------
Last modified on june 29th, 05


Open a console and type at the prompt the following
commands in order to install OpenCity on your
computer:


	mkdir obj
	cd obj
	../configure --enable-debug
	make
	make install


In case you don't have a configure script, the following
commands will creat one:


	aclocal
	automake
	autoconf


When the installation procedure have finished, you
can launch OpenCity from command-line with the
instructions below:


	cd $HOME/bin/opencity/bin
	./opencity


Have fun !
Duong-Khang (neoneurone) NGUYEN.
